<h2 id='get-balances'>Get Balances</h2>
<p><code>GET /balances/{account_id}</code></p>

<p>Fetches the balances of this account. Returns a mapping of asset symbols to their current balances.</p>
<h3 id='request'>Request</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Required</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>account_id</td>
<td>UUID</td>
<td>True</td>
<td>The account ID to fetch balances for</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<blockquote>
<p>Sample Response</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"BTC"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"1.21"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"ETH"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"5.67"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"SOL"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"10.11"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"USDC"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"1000.00"</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div><h3 id='response'>Response</h3>
<p>The response is a JSON object where:
- <strong>Keys</strong> are asset symbols (strings)
- <strong>Values</strong> are the current balance amounts (strings representing decimal numbers)</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Name</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>asset</td>
<td>String</td>
<td>The symbol of the asset (e.g., &quot;BTC&quot;, &quot;ETH&quot;, &quot;USDC&quot;)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>balance</td>
<td>String</td>
<td>The current balance amount as a decimal string</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
